    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 3rd level, you gain a pool of Mecha Dice which are d4's, equal to your Con mod. Spent Mecha Dice return after a long rest. You can spend a single die on your turn to increase the damage of a mecha-nin clan jutsu, gain a bonus to an ability check or saving throw to end an effect, or regain hit points, equal to the result of the roll.</p>",
